<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Arial;margin:0.0px;">
    <strong>§ 20. Sõiduki peatamine</strong>
</p>
<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Helvetica;margin:0.0px;">
    <span style="font:10.0px Arial;"><strong>ja parkimine</strong></span> ..................... 11
</p>
<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Arial;margin:0.0px;">
    <strong>§ 21. Sõiduki peatamis-</strong>
</p>
