<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Helvetica;margin:0.0px;">
    <span style="font:10.0px Arial;"><strong>teel</strong></span> ..................................... 14
</p>
<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Arial;margin:0.0px;">
    <strong>§ 23. Jalakäija</strong>
</p>
<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Arial;margin:0.0px;">
    <strong>kohustused lapse</strong>
</p>
<p style="color:#000000;font:10.0px Arial;margin:0.0px;">
    <strong>ohutuse tagamisel</strong><span style="font:10.0px Helvetica;"> ......... 15</span>
